According to Master and Elder Guo, Master Chu Min's memory may be hard to recover in a short amount of time.

45
00:03:39,599 --> 00:03:43,689
Fortunately, she still remembers that she had taught at Big Dipper.

46
00:03:43,690 --> 00:03:47,549
Master asked her to continue teaching at Yaoguang Peak when she is better.

47
00:03:47,549 --> 00:03:50,981
Hopefully, it will help her recover her memory.

48
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:57,741
That's good. Lu Ping can feel at ease then, too.

49
00:03:58,380 --> 00:03:59,960
Sister Qin.

50
00:04:00,461 --> 00:04:05,139
About the news of Master Chu Min, can you tell my brother after he's been healed?

51
00:04:05,139 --> 00:04:06,919
So he doesn't have to worry as much.

52
00:04:06,920 --> 00:04:09,601
Lu Ping can be cured? How?

53
00:04:09,601 --> 00:04:14,939
I've already talked to Elder Guo about how to do it. If we find the Two Form Flower, my brother can be cured.

54
00:04:14,939 --> 00:04:16,439
Two Form Flower?

55
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:20,299
The Two Form Flower can protect his meridians and make them bear the power of six pneumas.

56
00:04:20,299 --> 00:04:24,639
It was very hard but my father managed to plant one. My brother took it when he left the valley.

57
00:04:24,639 --> 00:04:26,861
Do you know where it is?

58
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:43,880
Sister Qin, are you all right?

59
00:04:48,840 --> 00:04:50,441
Su Tang.

60
