66
00:05:21,080 --> 00:05:26,741
I married Lu Ping last night. I don't want much.

67
00:05:26,741 --> 00:05:30,041
I just want to live a peaceful life for a few days.

68
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:33,081
I hope you can help me.

69
00:06:08,620 --> 00:06:13,671
God, why do you always have to play tricks on people?

70
00:06:15,100 --> 00:06:18,161
There's only one Two Form Flower.

71
00:06:18,780 --> 00:06:22,041
In order to save me, Lu Ping made me take it.

72
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:28,511
Now I am afraid all I can do is use my blood, a life for a life.

73
00:06:40,080 --> 00:06:41,841
Why?!

74
00:06:43,110 --> 00:06:46,691
Why out of the two of us can only one survive?

75
00:06:47,460 --> 00:06:51,441
Why can't you let us be selfish for once?

76
00:06:58,650 --> 00:07:01,681
I really don't want to leave him.

77
00:07:04,700 --> 00:07:07,621
I really don't want to leave him.

78
00:07:56,440 --> 00:08:00,439
Bandit, you said you would cook. Have you been well behaved?

79
00:08:10,220 --> 00:08:13,281
Lu Ping... Lu Ping!

80
00:08:26,080 --> 00:08:29,239
You can choose one pneuma to practice. Then reach two.

81
00:08:29,239 --> 00:08:31,741
Until you can use several pneuma.

82
00:08:32,640 --> 00:08:36,519
Your fists are not straight enough. How could you use pneumatic powers?

83
00:08:36,519 --> 00:08:40,479
Keep your wrists relaxed and your knees straight. Try one more time.

84
00:08:43,250 --> 00:08:45,001
Why are you here?

85
00:08:49,950 --> 00:08:52,541
I've learned the pneumatic powers.

86
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:54,269
- You're so great!
- You're so great!

87
00:08:54,270 --> 00:08:55,540
I want to join the army, too!

88
00:08:55,540 --> 00:08:56,719
I have to serve my country.

89
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:59,079
One by one. Don't rush.

90
00:09:15,190 --> 00:09:18,999
Why didn't you stay at home? What are you doing here?

91
00:09:19,680 --> 00:09:23,721
Came out to relax. I can't stay at home all day.

92
00:09:24,580 --> 00:09:26,261
How was Big Dipper?

93
00:09:30,330 --> 00:09:32,721
Looking at these children,

94
00:09:32,721 --> 00:09:37,659
I think of the days when I lived and practiced with my seniors and juniors.

95
00:09:37,659 --> 00:09:39,781
I felt like I should go to see Big Dipper.

96
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:50,801
I can go with you right now. Good timing, as Su Tang just got back, too.

97
00:10:12,800 --> 00:10:15,559
Su Tang. Sangsang came in the morning for a short time.

98
00:10:15,559 --> 00:10:19,399
What did you say to her? Why did she ignore everyone and run off?

99
00:10:19,399 --> 00:10:23,180
Has she seen the Two Form Flower? Can your brother survive?

100
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:27,141
Wei Tianqi, are you looking for a beating?

101
00:10:27,141 --> 00:10:30,481
Are you looking forward to my brother's recovery or death?

102
00:10:30,481 --> 00:10:35,519
I'm telling you. Even if my brother is gone today, there is no room for you.

103
00:10:35,519 --> 00:10:37,521
Who says I am gone?

104
00:10:38,720 --> 00:10:40,120
Brother!

105
00:10:44,500 --> 00:10:49,661
I am sorry. I shouldn't have left you alone in Carefree Valley.

106
00:10:49,661 --> 00:10:52,459
It's good to see you back. As long as you're alive.

107
00:10:53,620 --> 00:10:57,060
Sangsang, let's not disturb their sibling reunion.

108
00:11:04,140 --> 00:11:07,681
I don't want to hear the name of Sangsang anymore.

109
00:11:07,681 --> 00:11:11,241
Today, you can call her sister-in-law.

110
00:11:11,241 --> 00:11:14,260
You. Shameless.

111
00:11:19,060 --> 00:11:20,581
Master Chu Min.

112
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:27,341
You all can learn from Master Chu of Yaoguang Peak from now on.

113
00:11:27,341 --> 00:11:28,720
Yes.

114
00:11:29,860 --> 00:11:33,841
New? Your foundations aren't even solid.

115
00:11:33,841 --> 00:11:37,781
First run 50 laps before entering Yaoguang Peak.

116
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:41,280
Master.

117
00:11:41,280 --> 00:11:42,279
Brother, our Master—

118
00:11:42,280 --> 00:11:43,841
Master Chu Min.

119
00:11:45,760 --> 00:11:49,681
Don't call me "Master" if you aren't one of Yaoguang Peak.

120
00:11:55,440 --> 00:11:58,721
When did Big Dipper have such weak disciples?

121
00:12:38,920 --> 00:12:41,021
Senior, there's no harm in saying what you want to say.

122
00:12:42,060 --> 00:12:44,681
You've always been very frank anyway.

123
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:49,201
Your internal breathing is disordered.

124
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:52,761
Before, you could have lived for more than a month.

125
00:12:54,560 --> 00:12:56,221
But now…

126
00:12:57,520 --> 00:12:59,481
How many days does he have left?

127
00:13:01,280 --> 00:13:03,601
Three days, at most.

128
00:13:19,620 --> 00:13:22,501
I used to hate the pneuma confinement.

129
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:27,481
But now that I don't have it,

130
00:13:29,440 --> 00:13:31,601
I can't protect my own life.

131
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:37,861
This is probably retribution, isn't it?

132
00:13:46,160 --> 00:13:48,891
What if there was another chance for you?

133
00:13:50,600 --> 00:13:53,391
No one has a second chance.

134
00:13:54,420 --> 00:13:58,061
Just say it. What would you do?

135
00:13:58,620 --> 00:14:00,661
The times when I went down the wrong path,

136
00:14:02,120 --> 00:14:04,841
I would do differently.

137
00:14:12,520 --> 00:14:14,961
Unfortunately, there is no turning back when it comes to time.

138
00:14:18,880 --> 00:14:23,981
I will try cooking the porridge again. I'll ask Su Tang to help this time.

139
00:14:51,220 --> 00:14:55,581
Su Tang, I didn't tell you before.

140
00:14:55,581 --> 00:14:59,621
Now I've decided, I'm going to save your brother.

141
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:02,241
I need your help.

142
00:15:02,241 --> 00:15:06,121
Sister Qin, don't joke.

143
00:15:06,780 --> 00:15:10,059
I found out about all of it. You'll die.

144
00:15:13,840 --> 00:15:18,441
If the Two Form Flower was in your blood, would you give it to Lu Ping?

145
00:15:33,160 --> 00:15:35,781
You and my brother just got married.

146
00:15:35,781 --> 00:15:40,761
If something happens to you, my brother would rather die.

147
00:15:40,761 --> 00:15:46,141
I know he will be very sad. So I want you to accompany him.

148
00:15:46,960 --> 00:15:49,701
You're the one that's closest to him.

149
00:15:49,701 --> 00:15:54,341
For you, he'll continue to live his life well.

150
00:15:58,400 --> 00:16:00,140
There are some things that

151
00:16:00,880 --> 00:16:04,771
no matter how hard it is, you still have to do.

152
00:16:05,960 --> 00:16:08,921
I want him to live well.

153
00:16:08,921 --> 00:16:12,041
Live according to his heart's wishes.

154
00:16:15,960 --> 00:16:20,260
No. Qin Sang, are you insane?

155
00:16:20,260 --> 00:16:23,839
You're going to die for Lu Ping? I don't agree. Come with me.

156
00:16:23,839 --> 00:16:25,260
Tianqi.

157
00:16:27,560 --> 00:16:29,100
What did you call me?

158
00:16:29,100 --> 00:16:32,661
Tianqi, Shuo is also your hometown.

159
00:16:32,661 --> 00:16:35,741
You have your brothers and friends here.

160
00:16:35,741 --> 00:16:41,121
Now the war has begun. You don't want to lose them either. Do you?

161
00:16:43,760 --> 00:16:48,059
As one person, I can't do anything about it. But Lu Ping can.

162
00:16:50,620 --> 00:16:52,761
But I don't want to watch you die.

163
00:16:53,600 --> 00:16:55,101
Tianqi.

164
00:16:55,920 --> 00:17:00,520
Don't come over here. No matter what, I won't agree to it.

165
00:17:07,590 --> 00:17:11,841
Ever since you came to Big Dipper, you've changed a lot.

166
00:17:11,841 --> 00:17:14,721
You know we should focus on the bigger picture.

167
00:17:14,721 --> 00:17:18,951
I believe you will become a formidable and brave man in the future.

168
00:17:21,480 --> 00:17:23,581
This is my last wish.

169
00:17:25,830 --> 00:17:29,761
You will help me. Won't you?

170
00:17:40,860 --> 00:17:45,301
Sangsang, You know I won't turn you down.

171
00:17:46,120 --> 00:17:51,201
You know that whatever you say, I'll say yes to.

172
00:18:14,580 --> 00:18:16,080
How is everything?

173
00:18:17,200 --> 00:18:20,739
The disciple guarding him has been transferred by me. I just gave Lu Ping silver needles.

174
00:18:20,739 --> 00:18:22,981
It'll be half a day before he wakes up.

175
00:18:27,560 --> 00:18:31,160
Su Tang, watch the gate.

176
00:18:31,160 --> 00:18:34,861
No matter who comes, don't let them disturb us.

177
00:18:51,040 --> 00:18:55,441
Take care of yourself. I'm entrusting Lu Ping to you.

178
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:30,560
My master taught me medical skills. Don't worry.

179
00:20:30,560 --> 00:20:35,020
It won't hurt at all. It'll feel like you're asleep.

180
00:21:11,640 --> 00:21:13,140
Tianqi.

181
00:21:17,600 --> 00:21:19,520
Thank you.

