[Surpass Big Dipper]

196
00:22:47,320 --> 00:22:51,190
[Wind Taker Academy]

197
00:23:00,440 --> 00:23:01,841
Do you miss it?

198
00:23:26,560 --> 00:23:31,821
Now when I think back, that was the happiest time.

199
00:23:31,821 --> 00:23:36,501
Although anything could've happened at any time and I was running for my life each day,

200
00:23:39,080 --> 00:23:41,941
it wasn't as empty as it is now.

201
00:23:47,600 --> 00:23:52,881
That's good. This way I won't regret my decision now.

202
00:23:54,440 --> 00:23:59,340
Bandit, I can't go with you this time.

203
00:24:00,920 --> 00:24:04,721
But remember I will always be with you.

204
00:24:19,360 --> 00:24:20,961
Where are you going?

205
00:24:49,140 --> 00:24:52,919
Brother, you're awake. How do you feel?

206
00:24:52,919 --> 00:24:54,601
Where is Qin Sang?

207
00:24:56,480 --> 00:24:57,980
Qin Sang.

208
00:25:10,770 --> 00:25:13,829
He's regained the six pneumas and his meridians have been reshaped.

209
00:25:13,830 --> 00:25:17,131
This brat, he's got both his life and his martial arts back.

210
00:25:21,730 --> 00:25:25,779
Brother, be careful. Be careful.

211
00:25:28,480 --> 00:25:33,780
Su Tang, what happened? Where is Qin Sang?

212
00:25:47,440 --> 00:25:51,840
Where is Qin Sang? Su Tang.

213
00:25:54,380 --> 00:25:58,541
Tell me what happened. Su Tang.

214
00:25:59,600 --> 00:26:05,141
Your injury could only be saved by the Two Form Flower.

215
00:26:07,370 --> 00:26:12,581
Sister Qin took the Two Form Flower before. In order to save you,

216
00:26:14,540 --> 00:26:17,241
she switched your blood with hers.

217
00:26:20,780 --> 00:26:23,980
Brother. Brother.

218
00:26:23,980 --> 00:26:26,239
- Lu Ping!
- Brother.

219
00:28:24,370 --> 00:28:29,561
Bandit, I acted on my own this time.

220
00:28:31,120 --> 00:28:33,161
Do you blame me?

221
00:28:36,260 --> 00:28:38,021
I had wanted to blame you.

222
00:28:41,280 --> 00:28:43,381
But I get it now.

223
00:28:45,920 --> 00:28:47,761
The ladies of the Qin Family

224
00:28:49,400 --> 00:28:51,701
are like a raging fire.

225
00:28:53,400 --> 00:28:55,321
Strong and vigorous.

226
00:28:58,080 --> 00:29:00,261
No one can persuade you to do differently.

227
00:29:06,340 --> 00:29:08,411
Do you regret marrying me?

228
00:29:30,680 --> 00:29:32,201
I regret...

229
00:29:35,500 --> 00:29:37,601
not marrying you earlier.

230
00:29:42,990 --> 00:29:48,521
Will you promise me anything I ask for?

231
00:29:54,320 --> 00:29:59,981
The heavens or the earth, whatever you want.

232
00:30:06,940 --> 00:30:12,641
I want to go up and have a look at the highest place in Big Dipper.

233
00:31:37,720 --> 00:31:43,021
Lu Ping, the night is so quiet here.

234
00:31:44,320 --> 00:31:47,021
It's like the night we got married.

235
00:31:47,920 --> 00:31:51,091
It gives me the feeling that

236
00:31:51,091 --> 00:31:53,801
there are only two of us in this world.

237
00:31:59,680 --> 00:32:01,730
As long as you're willing,

238
00:32:03,600 --> 00:32:06,040
I'll always be by your side.

239
00:32:06,041 --> 00:32:08,021
Watching for as long as you wish.

240
00:32:14,400 --> 00:32:16,380
I won't let anyone disturb us.

241
00:32:16,380 --> 00:32:20,000
♫ Wait for a gust of wind to blow through
the youngster's sleeves ♫

